l degree of the object. Variable depth = visual separation of stelliums.' : 'Trait fin = degré réel exact de l\\'objet. Profondeur variable = séparation visuelle des stelliums.'}\n    </p>\n</div>`;\n\n// ── Légende (page 3) ──\nhtml += `<div class=\"force-page-break-legend\">\n    <div class=\"legend-grid\">\n        <div><div class=\"legend-title\">${isEN ? 'Planets and Objects' : 'Planètes et Objets'}</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">☉</span> Soleil</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">☽</span> Lune</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">☿</span> Mercure</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph glyph-bold-fix\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♀</span> Vénus</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph glyph-bold-fix\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♂</span> Mars</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♃</span> Jupiter</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♄</span> Saturne</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♅</span> Uranus</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♆</span> Neptune</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">♇</span> Pluton</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">⚷</span> Chiron</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">☊</span> Nœud Nord</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item\"><span class=\"legend-glyph\" style=\"color:#1F3864;\">⊕</span> Part de Fortune</div>\n            <div class=\"legend-item